--- !u!1001 &7718943717000595346
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 1998854339062817388}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 2336890993758213722, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Size.z
      value: 130
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: narrativeElements.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[0]'
      value: 'I am Ra, the Sun Eternal, Creator of the Universe and Bringer of Life. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[1]'
      value: Since the dawn of time my barque travels the skies at day
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[2]'
      value: and navigates the perilous currents of Duat - the underworld - at night.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Without me the souls who crossed the Western Horizon\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[4]'
      value: ...would be lost in the lightless vastness of the Realm of the Dead.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[5]'
      value: 'I, Ra, shall protect them against the legions of the Lord of Silence:
        Osiris.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[6]'
      value: I am their beacon in the darkness! I shall guide them to a new dawn
        in the hereafter!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[7]'
      value: On our way the souls will be tested by the legions of the Lord of Silence
        - Osiris.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[8]'
      value: Yet, in this they are not alone!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[9]'
      value: For I am their beacon in the darkness!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[10]'
      value: For I, Ra,  shall protect them and guide them to a new dawn in the hereafter!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7601399522617559833, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: NarrativeTrigger
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
