      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[0]'
      value: "The end of the first hour is nigh\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[1]'
      value: ... soon we will arrive at the first gate.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[2]'
      value: You did well along the way!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[3]'
      value: Now, gather your courage for the fiery pits of the Piercing of Embers...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'narrativeElements.Array.data[4]'
      value: 'where vile, fire spitting serpents and even greater dangers lurk in
        the dark! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4010995484050687883, guid: 2a7f4e83c8836b948a9f5e642432f61a, type: 3}
